readable.content: A man and woman walking down the street . A woman and man carrying bags walking along a road with others in the background . There are two girls in the foreground of a group of people and they are both carrying shoulder book bags . Two firends are at an outdoor concert , and one is searching for something in her blue bag . Two flamboyantly dressed people at a walk featuring hundreds of people .
